name: Motherhood
body: What does it mean to be a mother? This looks different to all of us. In this section it is so important that we dig into your personal view of what a mom looks like. Much of what we know about being maternal is taken from our families of origin. We will review and discuss this in detail during our time together. It is important to note that judgment is a toxic energy in a self discovery process. We are taking a close look at our past, present and future holding it gently without labeling or judging ourselves or those we love.
